text: FROM groves of spice,&& O'er fields of rice,
O'er fields of rice,&& Athwart the lotus-stream,
Athwart the lotus-stream,&& I bring for you,
I bring for you,&& Aglint with dew
Aglint with dew%% A little lovely dream.
A little lovely dream.&& Sweet, shut your eyes,
Sweet, shut your eyes,&& The wild fire-fiies
The wild fire-fiies%% Dance through the fairy neem;

From the poppy-bole%% For you I stole
For you I stole%% A little lovely dream.
A little lovely dream.&& Dear eyes, good-night,
Dear eyes, good-night,&& In golden light
In golden light%% The stars around you gleam;

On you I press%% With soft caress
